A printer prints 17 pages per minute. How many minutes will it take to print 200 pages? Express your answer to the nearest whole number.
inference:
1. Determine the number of pages printed in 1 minute: 17 pages
2. Divide the total number of pages to be printed (200 pages) by the number of pages printed in 1 minute (17 pages): 200 pages ÷ 17 pages/minute = 11.76 minutes
3. Round the answer to the nearest whole number: 12 minutes
Final Answer: \boxed{$12$}. I hope it is correct.
